what is the point overriding the cgroups directory mounted by Docker in the worker containers?
{quote}

Thanks for bringing that up [~miklos.szegedi@cloudera.com]. At the time, I believe it was required to allow systemd to run inside the containers. That overlap is confusing and likely not the behavior wanted/anticipated.
